FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775012614
OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FIn a statement to BBC Newsnight on
OL,8,FTuesday evening, they said they were
OL,9,F"hopeful that conversation with
OL,10,Fsurvivors and their families will
OL,11,Fcontinue to elicit decisive action
OL,12,Ffrom the British government against
OL,13,Fthe co-conspirators of Jeffrey
OL,14,FEpstein".
OL,16,F"King Charles III's visit will come at
OL,17,Fa deeply personal time for our
OL,18,Ffamily," the statement said.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@HO]xD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775012614
OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,F"His arrival comes just two days after
OL,8,Fthe one-year anniversary of the death
OL,9,Fof our beloved sister, Virginia
OL,10,FRoberts Giuffre.
OL,12,F"We strongly urge King Charles to meet
OL,13,Fwith us and survivors and hear what we
OL,14,Fhave to say. We are thankful to him
OL,15,Ffor heeding our sister's allegations
OL,16,Fagainst Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor,
OL,17,Fand for his decisive action in
OL,18,Fstripping his brother from his
OL,19,Fposition as a prince.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775012614
OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,F"Amanda and I are hopeful that
OL,8,Fconversation with survivors and their
OL,9,Ffamilies will continue to elicit
OL,10,Fdecisive action from the British
OL,11,Fgovernment against the co-conspirators
OL,12,Fof Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,14,F"Virginia spent her life fighting to
OL,15,Fhold these predators accountable; it
OL,16,Fis in her memory that we encourage the
OL,17,Fking to speak with us and survivors,
OL,18,Fand continue pursuing justice across
OL,19,Fthe United Kingdom."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
