PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775012614
OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FThe late Ms Giuffre, who died by
OL,8,Fsuicide last year, accused Andrew of
OL,9,Fsexual abuse, which he vehemently
OL,10,Fdenies.
OL,12,FUS congressman Ro Khanna wrote to the
OL,13,FKing on Monday also calling for him to
OL,14,Fmeet survivors privately during the
OL,15,Fstate visit, which will take place in
OL,16,Flate April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
