PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775012614
OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FHowever, it is understood that the
OL,8,Fcouple will not be able to meet
OL,9,Fsurvivors while there are ongoing UK
OL,10,Fpolice investigations into matters
OL,11,Frelated to Epstein.
OL,13,FAndrew, the former Duke of York, and
OL,14,FLord Peter Mandelson, the former UK
OL,15,Fambassador to the US, were arrested in
OL,16,FFebruary on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,17,Fpublic office over their connections
OL,18,Fwith the paedophile financier.
OL,20,FThey have since been released under
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
