CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775012614
OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,8,F(NPCC) announced on Tuesday that the
OL,9,Fpolice response to the release of the
OL,10,Fso-called Epstein files by the US
OL,11,FDepartment of Justice is to be
OL,12,F"stepped up".
OL,14,FA dedicated group will look at the
OL,15,F"scale, scope and nature of any
OL,16,Fpotential UK-based VAWG (violence
OL,17,Fagainst women and girls) offending
OL,18,Fwithin the files", the NPCC added.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@LO]wD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
