OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump declared the
OL,8,Ftrip will be a "momentous occasion" in
OL,9,Fa post on his Truth Social site,
OL,10,Fadding that there would be "a
OL,11,Fbeautiful Banquet Dinner" at the White
OL,12,FHouse on the evening of April 28.
OL,14,FHe also revealed the "historic state
OL,15,Fvisit" will take place over four days
OL,16,Ffrom April 27-30, despite Buckingham
OL,17,FPalace deciding not to release the
OL,18,Fexact dates in its own official
OL,19,Fannouncement.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@cO]rD@\OUsD@YO]vD@VOUwD@FO]
