OL,3,CFamily of Virginia Giuffre call on
OL,4,CKing to meet with them during US state
OL,5,Cvisit
OL,7,F"I look forward to spending time with
OL,8,Fthe King, whom I greatly respect. It
OL,9,Fwill be TERRIFIC!," Mr Trump added.
